<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٥٦ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">‌مُحَمَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2540">‌سَلَمَةَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6128">‌مُسْلِمًا</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٣٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْبَطِينَ ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2343">‌سَعِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">‌ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ تَطُوفُ بِالْبَيْتِ وَهِيَ عُرْيَانَةٌ،<span class="c5"> تَقُولُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الْيَوْمَ يَبْدُو بَعْضُهُ أَوْ كُلُّهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا بَدَا مِنْهُ فَلَا أُحِلُّهُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ فَنَزَلَتْ:</span> <span class="c3">{يَا بَنِي آدَمَ خُذُوا زِينَتَكُمْ عِنْدَ كُلِّ مَسْجِدٍ}</span>».<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>